        Checks if this point is greater than (or equal) to lower and smaller than (or equal) to upper.
        Parameters:
        lower - point this value should be greater than

        public static PointValue parse​(CharSequence text,
                               CSVHeaderInformation fieldsFromHeader)
        Parses the given text into a PointValue. The information stated in the header is saved into the PointValue unless it is overridden by the information in the text
        Parameters:
        text - the input text to be parsed into a PointValue
        fieldsFromHeader - must be a value obtained from parseHeaderInformation(CharSequence) or null
        Returns:
        a PointValue instance with information from the {@param fieldsFromHeader} and {@param text}
